post_text: News from STEM
shared_text:
River Rouge STEM Academy K-8
September 1 at 2:36 PM ·

URGENT MESSAGE: We have exceeded our expected amount of laptops to distribute for distance learning. Therefore, we are canceling our Technology Distribution for Thursday, September 3. Unfortunately, the expected delivery has been delayed. However, If you did not get a chance to pick up your child’s schedule, the schedule can still be picked up on Thursday from 9am-3pm. First and second grade materials may also be picked up at this time. We will send out a notice of when the laptops are available for pick up. We apologize for the inconvenience. We appreciate your understanding and patience. LaToiya Revell MrCoach Holly

The River Rouge Athletic Department invites everyone to the River Rouge vs. Southfield Christian basketball game on Saturday, February 2, 2019.

We are also inviting all former members of the River Rouge Basketball Championship Teams (Boys' and Girls') to be in attendance.

Let's celebrate our 20th Anniversary since the last state championship.

Further information will be coming regarding the Freshman basketball game on the same day. If you have any questions, feel free to contact the office at (313) 203-1538.
